metadata.name: The Dawn of The Martyr
metadata.description:
I can feel the wind blowing through.
I have witnessed all of the pain.
As I learn to forgive and let go.
If I lose myself for the sake of love.
Is it worth the sacrifice?
Will I be remembered as a martyr?

* * *
